### =========================
### GET ALL PRODUCTS
### =========================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json


### =========================
### CREATE BRAND
### =========================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products/newBrand
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "brandName": "Anta"
}


### =========================
### CREATE PRODUCT
### =========================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products/createProduct
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "modelName": "Air Zoom Pegasus 40",
